OL,3,CMan threw vacuum cleaner and told
OL,4,Cpolice 'I hope your children get raped'
OL,6,FFootage released by Cleveland Police
OL,7,Fcaptured Thomas Rogers smashing the
OL,8,Fwindow of a residential property with
OL,9,Fa vacuum cleaner
OL,11,FA man threw a vacuum cleaner through a
OL,12,Fhouse window and told a police officer
OL,13,F"I hope your children get raped"
OL,14,Fduring riots in Middlesbrough.
OL,16,FThomas Rogers, 22, was "overwhelmed by
OL,17,Fdistaste for what had happened in
OL,18,FSouthport" when he joined a 1,000-
OL,19,Fstrong protest that "quickly turned
OL,20,Fviolent" in the town on Sunday 4
OL,21,FAugust, a court heard.
