OL,3,CMan threw vacuum cleaner and told
OL,4,Cpolice 'I hope your children get raped'
OL,6,FHe then told the officer: "I hope your
OL,7,Fkids get raped, I hate the police."
OL,9,FA statement from a student who lives
OL,10,Fin the shared house where Rogers was
OL,11,Ffilmed throwing a vacuum cleaner
OL,12,Fthrough the window said he and his
OL,13,Fpartner had been left "feeling
OL,14,Fdifferently about the town they called
OL,15,Fhome and the people they lived
OL,16,Famongst".
OL,18,FThe landlord of the property, on Union
OL,19,FStreet, said: "I feel angry and
OL,20,Fdisappointed with the thugs,
OL,21,Fespecially the idiot with the hoover."
