OL,6,FIn mitigation, the court heard Rogers
OL,7,Fwas a "complex and vulnerable young
OL,8,Fman" who had grown up in care.
OL,10,FTabitha Buck, defending, said the
OL,11,Fattack in Southport "had a significant
OL,12,Feffect on him" and he was "overwhelmed
OL,13,Fby distaste at what had occurred and
OL,14,Fhis distaste at what he felt was a
OL,15,Flack of reaction by the police."
OL,17,FShe told the court there was "indirect
OL,18,Fracism at play there".
OL,20,FDozens of people have been arrested in
OL,21,Fconnection to unrest in Middlesbrough.
